HEADWORD: Coction
<hw>Coc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>coctio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Act of boiling.</def>⟦br⟧
